269 6 "Robin Betrayed! The Motive of the World Government!"Transliteration: "Uragira re ta Robin! Sekai Seifu no Omowaku!" (Japanese:裏切られたロビン! 世界政府の思惑!) Katsumi Tokoro Hirohiko Kamisaka June 25, 2006(2006-06-25)[n 6][15] September 7, 2014

Spandam tells Robin that her crew has come to save her and that he, despite the agreement between her and the CP9, plans on taking them prisoner. On the main road, the Straw Hats and the Franky Family proceed towards the Courthouse Plaza.Choppertalks with the king bull Sodom, who notes that Usopp did not make it onto his back. Meanwhile, frustrated with his inability to move forward, Luffy slingshots himself onto the courthouse roof. There,Bluenois awaiting his arrival.
